Label: Organisation Name
Description: This is an alias that can be used as your organisation name in the system that was set up for you

Label: Password Reset Email
Description: This is the email that gets sent when a new password has been requested by a user

Label: Account Created Email
Description: This is the email that gets sent to any user advises an account has been created for them. Provides a link to set a password

Label: Final Package Email
Description: This is the email that gets sent to subscribed parties when an offer has been submitted

Label: Bulk Applicant Email
Description: This is the email that gets sent to applicants when using the bulk offer function in Onboard from a partner

Label: KYC Individual Invite Email
Description: This is the email that gets sent to individuals when they are requested to complete a KYC check

Label: KYC Link Already Completed Message
Description: This is the message displayed at the top of a form when a customer has already completed their KYC but accesses the link sent to them again

Label: KYC Link Expired Message
Description: This is the message that will show on the page when the link associated with KYC has expired

Label: KYC Link SMS message
Description: This is the SMS that gets sent to an applicant requesting them to complete the KYC process

Label: Officer Approval Required Email
Description: If you are a listed approver, and your approval is required for any reason, this is the email that is sent to inform you

Label: Check In Alert Email
Description: This is the email that gets sent to users every 30 days to keep their account active gives a 5 day time period to keep active. This ensures security by preventing users from gaining access to Onboard after they leave their roles etc.

Label: Offer Note Reply Email Notification Body
Description: If you are subscribed to an offer, this is the email that will be sent when a new note has been put on the offer

Label: Verification Note Reply Email Notification Body
Description: If you have permission to view verifcation notes, and you have subscribed to a verification, this email advises that a new note has been added

Label: New Verification Note Email Notification Body
Description: If you have subscribed to a verification, and a new verification note is inputted, this is the template that will be used in the email.

Label: Offer Subscription - Verification Started Email Body
Description: This is the email that gets sent when a user is subscribed to an offer and the verification for that offer has been started

Label: Offer Subscription - Verification Completed Email Body
Description: This is the email that gets sent when a user is subscribed to an offer and the verification for that offer has been completed

Label: Offer Subscription - New Note Added Email Body
Description: When subscribed to an offer and a new offer note is placed on it, this email is sent to the subscriber

Label: Offer Subscription - Offer Completed Email Body
Description: If you are subscribed to an offer, this is the email that will be sent when the offer has been completed

Label: Payment Invoice Email
Description: The system has the ability to take payments form applicants in offers, this is the payment invoice email that provides a tax invoice for their payment

Label: OCDD Daily Alert Email
Description: If you have been set up to be flagged if there is an OCDD alert, this is the email that is sent to notify that action is required

Label: Login Page Content
Description: This is where you can customize the login page for your partner specific instance of Onboard

Label: List Export Completed Email
Description: If you have requested an export from the system, this is the email sent informing you the export is complete and ready to be downloaded

Label: List Export Failed Email
Description: If you have requested an export from the system, this is the email sent informing you the export has been failed

Label: Communications Mail Signature
Description: This is the footer that goes on the bottom of any communications email

Label: Lost Email Reply
Description: Should someone respond directly to the system without using the code located in the subject of the email, this is the reply stating that they have sent an email to an unmonitored email inbox

Label: Verification Workflow Update Completed
Description: If a verification workflow is updated, and the option to update existing workflows is selected, this is the email sent informing that the update has been completed

Label: External Approval Mail
Description: When the system requires approval from someone who isn't an OnBoard user, this is the email that will be sent to them

Label: KYC Form Text For Authorized Signatory
Description: If using old forms, this is where you change the KYC welcome text for the authorised signatory, which kicks off as soon as an application has been completed

Label: KYC Form Title  For Authorized Signatory
Description: This is the title of KYC welcome page for the authorised signatory

Label: Declaration Information Collection Welcome Title
Description: This is the title displayed on the welcome page of a declaration form

Label: Declaration Information Collection Welcome Content
Description: If you are using declarations, and non-smart forms, this is where the declaration welcome page content can be edited

Label: Individual Declaration Welcome Text
Description: This sets the declaration welcome page text

Label: Individual KYC Welcome Text
Description: This sets the declaration welcome page text

Label: Declaration Form Finished Text
Description: This is the text that will be displayed when a declaration form has been completed successfully by an individual

Label: KYC Individual Form Finished Text
Description: This sets the text of the 'You're all finished' section of KYC individual form

Label: Verifier Assigned Email
Description: This is the email that gets sent to a verifier when they have been assigned a verification from a partner via OnBoard

Label: Declaration Information Collection Email
Description: This is the email that gets sent to related individuals when a declaration is used and the link is sent to the related individual

Label: Declaration Form Finished Text - Secondary Signatories
Description: This is the text displayed on the page for second signatories once they have signed

Label: Auto-Distillation Customer Help Modal
Description: This is the content that is displayed in the help modal when an applicant is presented with the requirement to provide the Beneficial Owners of the organisation and their details.

Label: Book A Meeting Module Text
Description: This is the text that is displayed at the top of the customer form if the calendar link is enabled.

Label: Individual KYC Welcome Text
Description: If you are doing an individual KYC, this sets the welcome text of that page

Label: Email sent to applicant to collect payment for application.
Description: This is the email that gets sent to applicants if payment collection is enabled within the platform

Label: New Offer Note Email Notification Body
Bulk User Assigned as Action Owner Email
Description: This is the email that will be sent to you when you are bulk assigned as the Action Owner for multiple records.

Label: User Assigned as Action Owner Email
Description: This is the email that will be sent to you when you are assigned as the Action Owner for a record.

Label: Action Owner reassigned on Record Email
Description: This is the email that will be sent to you have requested an update to the Action Owner on a record.

Label: Action has been completed on a Record Email
Description: This is the email that will be sent to you when you have requested an update to the Action completion status on a record.
